Kepubify converts ePubs to kepubs (Kobo's ebook format).

Features:

- Full support of all kepub features
- Batch conversion
- Fast (about 12x faster than Calibre)
- Works from the command line
- Update Kobo series metadata
- Does not add any extra metadata (unlike Calibre)
- Supports many different CSS tweaks

WWW: https://geek1011.github.io/kepubify/
